  "title": "Violin Teacher (Part -time)",
  "description": "<h3>Violin Teacher (Part-Time)</h3><p>We are hiring Violin Part-Time Teachers who share our long-term vision and are eager to grow with us.<br /></p><p>📍 Location: <strong>Central Region</strong>, Singapore</p><h3>🎼 Responsibilities:</h3><ul><li>Conduct engaging individual and group violin lessons.</li><li>Attend school development programs when required.</li><li>Prepare students for performances, recitals, and competitions.</li><li>Guide students through examination preparations (e.g., ABRSM, Trinity, etc.).</li><li>Participate in company events such as music recitals and charity concerts.</li><li>Record tutorial and performance videos for marketing purposes if needed.</li></ul><h3>🎵 Requirements:</h3><ul><li>Passionate about teaching and nurturing students through music.</li><li>Committed to continuous personal and musical development.</li><li>Degree or diploma in Music Education, Performing Arts, or equivalent.</li><li>Proficient in English; candidates who can speak Mandarin will have an advantage (to liaise with Mandarin-speaking associates).</li><li>No prior experience is required, but at least 1-2 years of teaching experience is an advantage.</li></ul><p>If you love music education and want to make a meaningful impact on students' musical journeys, we’d love to hear from you!<br /></p>",
